skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pick one between
des:
Have you been in any of the following situations?
- Stuck with a friend that always says, "I'm cool with anything".
- Can't decide if you want to go to the beach or a hike on a Saturday.
- Can't make up your mind if you should gift your spouse an Amazon Echo or an Apple Watch for their birthday.

By the time you are faced with such a situation, you typically have two options that you or your group needs to decide on.

Look no further! Just ask Alexa to "Pick One Between" the two options and voila!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
